<lyrics>[V1]
 (mn kl qlby yạ rb bạjy .. wbạḥṭ qlby qdạm ʿynyk
 bạksẖf lk ṭrqy wḥyạty .. wạstny̱ yạ rb ʿml ạ̹ydyk)2
 (bạstny̱ wạtẖbt ạ̉nẓạry ʿlyk .. wtgẖyr ṣwrty bʿml ạ̹ydyk
 wmạdmt fyã wmạdmt fyk .. hạykml qlby mtmsk byk)2
